$ s X(s) + g / R X(s) = U(s), med x(0) = 0 $

从而有，开环传递函数$G(s)$

$ G(s) = frac(X(s), U(s)) = frac(1, s + g/R) $

当$u(t) = C$，则

$ lim_(t → ∞) h = C R / g $

